column5: Just around the corner from Zilker Park and the famous Barton Springs. Only three miles from downtown/ the heart of Austin. There's Taco Deli and corner store with beer, groceries and essentials just a two minute around the corner. You can also gain access to beautiful hiking trails along the green belt just at the end of the street. In addition to the queen size bed there is a couch and queen size air mattress.
